title: Chitose etc.
sinopse:
Chitose is a high school student who lives in Okinawa, so what will she do, when she falls in love with a student from Tokyo, Koushu…? Even if my love is one sided, “I’ll transfer to Tokyo,” so she leaves Okinawa for Tokyo. Chitose, don’t you think love is naturally mutual?!

(Source: Midnight Scans)
